
simple-bar is splitted in 4 main widgets:

> Current process name (app name & title)

> Spaces display
  - Show each space
  - Highlight current space
  - Show each app in each space
  - Highlight current app in current space
  - Go to space on Click

  - With SIP disable: create, move, destroy workspace

> Global information
  - Current Browser track
  - Spotify current track with track state (play/pause), toggle state on click
  - Dynamic battery level
  - Microphone on/off toggle
  - Dynamic sound indicator
  - Wifi network name, toggle wifi on click
  - Today date
  - Current time with day progress indicator from midnight to midnight

> Settings module
  - Customize bar layout
  - Enable/disable individual global information widgets
  - Try it out to discover every possibilities